Merge pull request #1 from da7th/da7th-patch-1

Update README.md

Update README.md

Docs - Format of title's Headings

Explicitly use version major and minor for version control

Optimised code for TF 1.0.1 as well. We only check major and minor
version number now. Everything < 0.11 uses different key name

explicitly name variable

In TF 1.0 the order for the variables in tf.concat are changed. By
explicitly naming the inputs we ensure that the code works for all
versions.

Add support for TF 1.0 in version control convolution.py

The if-statement is to general, by including the complete version
number we assure that the correct key is loaded for TF 1.0 as well.

Corrected column order of header row

The correct column names for the coordinates are xmin, ymin, xmax, ymax in this order.

Corrected data format

The order of the coordinates for the crowdAI dataset is actually xmin, ymin, xmax, ymax (as opposed to xmin, xmax, ymin, ymax as it was stated before)
